[Nouns] convergence, confluence, concourse, conflux, congress, concurrence, concentration; convergency; appulse, meeting; corradiation.
assemblage [more]; resort (focus) [more]; asymptote.
[Verbs] converge, concur, come together, unite, meet, fall in with; close with, close in upon; center round, center in; enter in; pour in.
gather together, unite, concentrate, bring into a focus.
[Adjectives] converging; convergent, confluent, concurrent; centripetal; asymptoptical, asymptoptic; confluxible.
